  notes: >-
    Submitted. Preprint and reproducibility package available at the
    repository above. Version 2.8 supersedes v2.7 with Sprint 1-13
    simulator hardening (country-alias normalisation, realism-gate
    fix, agent-prompt + engine improvements) and a re-calibration on
    the same 42 empirical scenarios (test MAE 19.18 → 17.56 pp,
    coverage₉₀ 75.0% → 87.5%; see §10 of the paper).
